## **Purpose**
Re-test the updated Booking System (Phase 2) to verify whether the vulnerabilities identified in Phase 1 and Part 2 were fixed.

## **Scope**
- **Tested:** Login page, registration page (if enabled), database storage, HTTP communication, security headers, CSRF protection, OWASP ZAP Round 3  
